      <front>
         <p>
            <address>
               <addrLine>To</addrLine>
               <addrLine>D<hi rend="super">r</hi> Thomas Wharton MD:</addrLine>
               <addrLine>in Kings-Arms Yard</addrLine>
               <addrLine>Coleman Street</addrLine>
               <addrLine>London</addrLine>
            </address>
            <stamp type="postmark">
               <date>4 MA</date>
            </stamp>
         </p>
      </front>
      <body>
         <opener>
            <dateline>Thursday Ã¢&#x80;&#x93; Camb:e.</dateline>
            <salute>Dear doctor </salute>
         </opener>
         <p>I accept with pleasure your kind invitation, &amp; have agreed to accompany Mr Balguy &amp; Mr Hurd
					to Town on Saturday. what I have farther to say, I defer to that time: I need not tell you how much I
					wish for it, or that I am ever</p>
         <closer>
            <salute>Sincerely Yours </salute>
            <signed>TG:</signed>
         </closer>
         <postscript>
            <p>My best Compliments to Mrs Wharton. </p>
         </postscript>
      </body>
